<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.2">
<l>āviyē yamutē yeṉaniṉain turuki</l>
<l>yavaravarp paṇaimulai tuṇaiyā</l>
<l>pāviyē ṉuṇarā tettaṉai pakalum</l>
<l>paḻutupō yoḻintaṉa nāḷkaḷ</l>
<l>tūvicē raṉṉam tuṇaiyoṭum puṇaruñ</l>
<l>cūḻpuṉaṟ kuṭantaiyē toḻuteṉ</l>
<l>nāviṉā luyya nāṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Thinking, “my life, my nectar,” and melting</l>
<l rend="indent">with the companionship of many full-breasted women,</l>
<l>Without realizing [it], wretched me,</l>
<l rend="indent">how many days [worth] of time has gone wasted in ruin?</l>
<l>Worshipping in Kuṭantai, encircled by water where</l>
<l rend="indent">a feathered swan joins with its mate,</l>
<l>For my tongue to save [me], I discovered for myself</l>
<l rend="indent">the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
